            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-142] Provide Javadoc as to the maximum size of the data byte array that may be stored within a znode</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-142</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently there is nothing in the API documentation as to the maximum size of the data in a znode.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
